<template>
  <v-row>
    <v-dialog
      v-model="dialog"
      persistent
      max-width="290"
    >
      <template v-slot:activator="{ on, attrs }">
        <v-btn
          color="red"
          dark
          v-bind="attrs"
          v-on="on"
          text
        >
          Excluir
        </v-btn>
      </template>
      <v-card>
        <v-card-title class="text-h5">
          Confirmar exclusão?
        </v-card-title>
        
        <v-card-actions>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn
            color="red"
            plain
            @click="dialog = false"
          >
            Não
          </v-btn>
          <v-btn
            color="primary"
            depressed
            @click="removeProductById()"
          >
            Sim
          </v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
      </v-card>
    </v-dialog>
  </v-row>
</template>

<script>
import {deleteProduct} from '../../services/api'
  export default {
    data () {
      return {
        dialog: false,
      }
    },
    props: ['productId'],
    methods: {
        removeProductById(){
            const productId = this.productId
            deleteProduct(productId)
            .then( res => {
                if(res.status == 200) {
                    console.log(res.status);
                }
            })
            this.dialog = false
        }
    }
  }
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
